Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.77,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.07,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.89,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.51,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.28,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.98,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.23,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:41.99,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.53,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.74,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:02:00.08,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.85,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.52,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.23,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.89,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.52,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.06,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.98,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.64,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.71,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.91,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.00,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.19,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.54,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:39.82,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.75,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered\Njust before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around\Nthe world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered\Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having defeated\NDuval's Flying Fish Riders,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy and company\Nnow head for Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't mean\Nyou're suddenly somehow forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering how it tastes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! It is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, there are actually two routes\Nthat lead to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for outlaws like you guys,\Nthere's really only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just maintain course\Nfor the route you'll use,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is known as Fish-Man Island's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sea Floor Route"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Line is a large barrier\Nthat stretches all around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there is one small hole\Nin one part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's where Fish-Man Island is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make their ship\Ncapable of submerging to the sea floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and company\Nneeded to visit a certain island first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It came outta the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm riding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's our purpose\Non this island, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're going to see\Na coating craftsman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have him cover your ship in resin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, that'll make it\Nso your ship can go underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so Luffy and company landed\Non the Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to find a coating craftsman Hachi knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tyranny! The Rulers of Sabaody,\Nthe Celestial Dragons"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gone into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, we used up all the cola\Nin that last sea battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's maintenance is my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm stayin' behind\Nbecause I wanna help, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all three of us\Ngo when we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wait for someone to come back\Nand then go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because my beloved\NNami-san said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever will I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is so full\Nof treasure right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish there was a knight somewhere\Nwho could protect it for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know how to fall\Nright into Nami's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a slave of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admitting it yourself saves me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth to Zoro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going all by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare, you damn bastard!\NYou always get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an archipelago, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never be able to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if anyone could get lost on such\Nstraightforward islands as these!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the trees are numbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worst case, even a kid could make\Nit back by asking for directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you\Nto have such street-smarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We underestimated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to ask for directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trust yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what the hell\Nthey're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to remember\Nthis tree's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#1. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can mock me all they want;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get lost on these islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike some other guy\Nwith no sense of direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Nobles are also known\Nas the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They act so high and mighty\Nthat they wear masks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep from breathing\Nthe same air as common people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do, don't defy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one thing you have to promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a couple other things\Nto watch out for, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I mentioned before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people heading for the New World\Ngather on these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are infamous\Npirates like you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as marines and bounty hunters\Nwho are out to catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no law here at all\Nagainst buying and selling pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do anything to stand out\Nand they'll set their sights on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so be very careful what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The marines here\Naren't pushovers, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters is in\Nnearby waters, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why the bounty hunters\Nare all just as ferocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one other thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many things\Nto watch out for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when did you get hurt there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie and I aren't merfolk\Nor fish-men here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat us like we're human\Non these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make things a lot simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When in a city,\Ndo as its citizens do, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do as Mr. Octopus says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harder! And push into it slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get in! I can get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not leaking at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put this inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that high enough for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go forward now if you peddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's going forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really doesn't pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Convenient, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Sabaody Archipelago's\Nfamous Bubble Bikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna ride too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 500 Berries a day to rent one,\Nor 10,000 Berries to buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty cheap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll rent--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy this one\Nwith my spending money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just rent.\NThere's no point in buying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get to decide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh! I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rent two more, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're from around these parts?\NWhat a bummer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it, though?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even have different kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me want to sing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm gonna buy\Na Bubble Bike after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you first went up\Ninto the sky on those bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come falling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Actually, I went\Npast the tops of the trees
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wondered if I could\Ngo any higher up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when all the bubbles\Naround me disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the bubble I was on\Nsuddenly popped too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have left\NSabaody Archipelago's climate area, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has a suitable climate\Nfor Hustle Mustle Mangroves to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside that area,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the resin components in the bubbles\Nlose a lot of their capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means the bubbles\Ncan't be ridden outside of these islands?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newcomers here often buy Bubble Bikes\Nand take them with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dirty business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renting Bubble Bikes is all you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm buying one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I can't agree\Nwith that explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't understand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the bubbles will pop\Noutside of these islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mysteriously enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They pop mysteriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been trying to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can use it on\NFish-Man Island, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bubble civilization\Non the sea floor, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go to Fish-Man Island\Nright away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should meet\Nthe Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a girl of matchless beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a panderer; shall I hook you up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love having an eyeful\Nof beautiful girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I lack eyes,\Ndue to being a skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, that smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a "Grand-Bun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.12,On Top,sign,0000,0000,0000,,"Grand-Bun" "GR Famous Food"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.37,On Top,sign,0000,0000,0000,,"GR Famous Grand-choco!!"\N"GR Famous Grand-Bun!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:13:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Line Manju buns!\NCommonly called Grand-Buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a taste test?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See how they say\N"Grandline First Half" here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very popular as souvenirs\Nfor going into the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They last for three whole months,\Nso you can rest easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you to open the next box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to pay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grove #35.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seem to be a lot of hotels here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're for the sailors who're waiting\Nfor their passes from Marie Jois.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Building hotels is easy, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paint a giant bubble with a metal alloy\Nand you have your foundation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how round buildings are made!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Is that a shopping mall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand-cracker! Grand-choco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keychain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pennant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are all about the memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really bought a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be tough to lug all that around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have 'im bubble pack it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubble pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need strength\Nto carry stuff on these islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are Nami and Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went to the shopping mall\Nin Grove #30.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left us in charge\Nof getting the ship coated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? They did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we headed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grove #13.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a ways away,\Neven by Bubble Bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie-chan didn't come along\Nwhen we invited her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been a bit reserved\Never since we landed on these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's up with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, perhaps this island\Nhas a bad history...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad history?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the lead now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a long way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did this suddenly\Nturn into a race?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-uhh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Take...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...going back home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Hey!\NI beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just lend me an axe or a saw
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to break this collar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given up on the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a wife and kid back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Please!\NHelp me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My kid was just a baby back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bugger still doesn't\Neven know what I look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably a pirate who was caught\Nby kidnappers and then sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His owners brought him to this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then he ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he surely knows\Nthere's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this collar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only... If only it wasn't for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slaves always have leashes\Naround their necks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are set to explode if the slaves\Ntry to remove them and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna buy souvenirs and go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving up the pirate business...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an escaped slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! We need to help that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised not to get involved,\Nno matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are Celestial Dragons nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay calm, Camie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down from the Bubble Bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Celestial Dra--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kneel down, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever comes,\Ndon't look them in the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same for you guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! How disgraceful, Saruu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one has broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you remember to give it\Na sedative every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I most certainly did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has no effect on the poor fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please buy me a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible at taking care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep breaking everything\Nin my ship captain collection...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this thing's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A grown man, always crying\Nabout family this, family that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he's nothing but a mere human!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not doing anything now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's--!\N--Stop! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I would like\Na giant for a slave next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you will start with a human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like such weak ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just endure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get out of here for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will help you relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel very good now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he'll survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he does,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll probably go to prison,\Nseeing that he's a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pirate could've easily\Nbeaten that old man and lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harm a Celestial Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a Navy HQ admiral\Nwill lead an entire army here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An admiral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aokiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could even be Akainu or Kizaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters\Nis very close by, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes them so high and mighty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They share the Creators' blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creators?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The twenty kings who created the huge\NWorld Government organization
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,800 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their descendents are\Nthe Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With each passing generation,\Nthey grow more reckless with power,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is why they act like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,300 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.19,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakky's Rip-Off Bar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey-chan, is it? Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I would know of the 300 million Berries, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are currently,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people with higher bounties than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higher than Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Rivals Gather! The 11 Supernovas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
